_sText:
The Lobby has a lot of doors, which teleports you in different rooms
in different style with different hidespots.
You should run it with more than 32 People at least. 
Recommended are 64 Players.

The map should run fine. There is a secret. Slow-Motion.
Try to find out, how to activate it. If you want, I can PM you the
solution.

Have Fun!
